			</svg>
			   I'm Aashiq
		</div>
		
		<div class="text-center mt-1">
			I like computer graphics, spatial computing, <span class="hidden sm:inline"><br></span>
			and immersive storytelling
		</div> 

		
		
		<div class=" mt-12 text-center underline">
			<a class="" href="/assets/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" >view my <span class="font-bold tracking-wide">resume</span>
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="inline w-4 h-4 stroke-2 -translate-y-0.5">
